  "texts": [
    "Beyond improvements over the base model, we also examine whether merging can surpass the strongest individual fine-tuned checkpoint.",
    "As shown in Table 2, Task Arithmetic reliably exceeds the best expert for three of the four model families once n ≥ 4.",
    "For example, in Qwen-4B, TA delivers a +1.02 improvement at n=4, which increases steadily to +1.72 at n=12.",
    "Qwen-8B shows an almost identical pattern, with gains rising from +1.14 at n=4 to +1.49 at n=12.",
    "Llama-3B also surpasses its best expert once n ≥ 4, improving from +0.32 at n=4 to +0.82 at n=12."
  ],
